<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>منصة جسور | أول حاضنة أعمال مدرسية ذكية</title>
    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- AOS Animation -->
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-blue: #1E3A8A;
            --primary-blue-dark: #0F2A6B;
            --primary-green: #10B981;
            --primary-green-dark: #059669;
            --primary-orange: #F59E0B;
            --primary-orange-dark: #D97706;
            --primary-purple: #8B5CF6;
            --primary-teal: #06B6D4;
            --gray-bg: #F3F4F6;
            --gray-card: #FFFFFF;
            --gray-border: #E5E7EB;
            --text-dark: #1F2937;
            --text-light: #6B7280;
            --text-white: #FFFFFF;
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --shadow-lg: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --radius-sm: 8px;
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --radius-lg: 24px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--gray-bg);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* English Mode */
        body.english {
            direction: ltr;
            text-align: left;
        }

        body.english .lang-ar {
            display: none;
        }

        body:not(.english) .lang-en {
            display: none;
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: var(--gray-card);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px 0;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-green));
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-green));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 28px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .lang-toggle {
            background: var(--gray-bg);
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .lang-toggle:hover {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--primary-green-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-green);
            color: var(--primary-green);
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320"><path fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,96L48,112C96,128,192,160,288,160C384,160,480,128,576,122.7C672,117,768,139,864,154.7C960,171,1056,181,1152,165.3C1248,149,1344,107,1392,85.3L1440,64L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path></svg>') no-repeat bottom;
            background-size: cover;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* Cards */
        .section {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--gray-card);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-border);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-green));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Stats */
        .stats {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-green));
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* Problems Bank */
        .problems-section {
            background: var(--gray-bg);
        }

        .filters {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .filter-btn {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid var(--gray-border);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        .filter-btn.active, .filter-btn:hover {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .problem-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 24px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .problem-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .problem-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--primary-orange);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .problem-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .problem-desc {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .problem-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-border);
        }

        .adopt-btn {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Steps */
        .steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .step {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 200px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
        }

        /* Testimonials */
        .testimonial-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .testimonial-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-blue);
        }

        /* CTA */
        .cta {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--primary-purple));
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .cta h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: var(--text-dark);
            color: var(--text-light);
            padding: 60px 0 30px;
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            display: block;
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-icons a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .copyright {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 32px;
            }
            .section-title {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .nav {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }

        /* Modal */
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            z-index: 2000;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background: white;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 32px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .fade-up {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <div class="logo">
                    <div class="logo-icon">ج</div>
                    <div class="logo-text">جسور | Jusur</div>
                </div>
                <div class="nav">
                    <a href="#home" class="lang-ar">الرئيسية</a>
                    <a href="#home" class="lang-en">Home</a>
                    <a href="#problems" class="lang-ar">بنك المشكلات</a>
                    <a href="#problems" class="lang-en">Problems Bank</a>
                    <a href="#program" class="lang-ar">برنامج الاحتضان</a>
                    <a href="#program" class="lang-en">Incubation</a>
                    <a href="#about" class="lang-ar">عن المنصة</a>
                    <a href="#about" class="lang-en">About</a>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px;">
                    <button class="lang-toggle" onclick="toggleLanguage()">
                        <span class="lang-ar">English</span>
                        <span class="lang-en">العربية</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="openModal()">
                        <span class="lang-ar">انضم الآن</span>
                        <span class="lang-en">Join Now</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero" id="home">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1 class="lang-ar">منصة جسور – من المشكلة إلى المشروع</h1>
                    <h1 class="lang-en">Jusur Platform – From Problem to Project</h1>
                    <p class="lang-ar">أول حاضنة أعمال مدرسية ذكية تربط الطلاب بالمشكلات الحقيقية ورواد الأعمال والمتخصصين والمستثمرين</p>
                    <p class="lang-en">The first smart school business incubator connecting students with real problems, entrepreneurs, specialists, and investors</p>
                    <div class="hero-buttons">
                        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('problems').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">
                            <span class="lang-ar">اكتشف بنك المشكلات</span>
                            <span class="lang-en">Explore Problems Bank</span>
                        </button>
                        <button class="btn-outline" onclick="openModal()">
                            <span class="lang-ar">انضم كمرشد</span>
                            <span class="lang-en">Join as Mentor</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Stats Section -->
        <section class="stats">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div>
                        <div class="stat-number">50,000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-ar">طالب مستفيد</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-en">Students Impacted</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="stat-number">1,000+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-ar">مرشد وخبير</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-en">Mentors & Experts</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-ar">مشروع ممول</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-en">Funded Projects</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-ar">مدرسة مشاركة</div>
                        <div class="stat-label lang-en">Participating Schools</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title lang-ar">مميزات منصة جسور</h2>
                <h2 class="section-title lang-en">Jusur Platform Features</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle lang-ar">نقدم لك تجربة متكاملة لتحويل أفكارك إلى مشاريع حقيقية</p>
                <p class="section-subtitle lang-en">A complete experience to turn your ideas into real projects</p>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">بنك المشكلات</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Problems Bank</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">آلاف المشكلات الحقيقية التي تحتاج حلولاً مبتكرة</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Thousands of real problems waiting for innovative solutions</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">مطابقة ذكية</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Smart Matching</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">خوارزميات ذكاء اصطناعي تربطك بالمرشد المناسب</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">AI algorithms connect you with the right mentor</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-robot"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">مساعد ذكي 24/7</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">AI Assistant 24/7</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">مرشد رقمي يساعدك في كل خطوة</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Digital mentor guiding you every step</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">نظام التلعيب</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Gamification</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">نقاط وشارات وجوائز تحفيزية</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Points, badges, and exciting rewards</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-store"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">السوق المصغر</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Mini-Market</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">عرض وبيع النماذج الأولية</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Showcase and sell your prototypes</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-icon"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-user"></i></div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">سفراء جسور</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Jusur Ambassadors</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">خريجون يوجهون الجيل القادم</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Graduates guiding the next generation</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Problems Bank Section -->
        <section class="section problems-section" id="problems">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title lang-ar">بنك المشكلات</h2>
                <h2 class="section-title lang-en">Problems Bank</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle lang-ar">اختر مشكلة حقيقية وكن جزءاً من الحل</p>
                <p class="section-subtitle lang-en">Choose a real problem and be part of the solution</p>
                
                <div class="filters">
                    <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterProblems('all')"><span class="lang-ar">الكل</span><span class="lang-en">All</span></button>
                    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProblems('tech')"><span class="lang-ar">تقني</span><span class="lang-en">Tech</span></button>
                    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProblems('edu')"><span class="lang-ar">تعليمي</span><span class="lang-en">Education</span></button>
                    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProblems('env')"><span class="lang-ar">بيئي</span><span class="lang-en">Environment</span></button>
                    <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterProblems('health')"><span class="lang-ar">صحي</span><span class="lang-en">Health</span></button>
                </div>

                <div class="grid" id="problemsGrid">
                    <!-- Problems will be loaded via JS -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- How It Works -->
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title lang-ar">كيف تعمل منصة جسور؟</h2>
                <h2 class="section-title lang-en">How Jusur Works?</h2>
                <div class="steps">
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">اختر مشكلة</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Choose a Problem</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">تصفح بنك المشكلات واختر التحدي الذي يناسبك</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Browse the Problems Bank and pick your challenge</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">سجل فكرتك</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Submit Your Idea</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">قدم فكرتك واحصل على تقييم فوري من المساعد الذكي</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Submit your idea and get instant AI feedback</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                        <h3 class="lang-ar">احصل على مرشد</h3>
                        <h3 class="lang-en">Get a Mentor</h3>
                        <p class="lang-ar">تطابق مع رائد أعمال أو متخصص في مجالك</p>
                        <p class="lang-en">Match with an entrepreneur or expert in your field</p>
                    </div>
